OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain for
OL,7,FOrkney which will spread across
OL,8,FShetland too. Becoming rather misty
OL,9,Finto the early hours with further
OL,10,Fshowery outbreaks of rain expected.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA rather cloudy and damp start
OL,13,Fto the morning with light and patchy
OL,14,Frain. Becoming drier through the day
OL,15,Fwith some bright or sunnier spells
OL,16,Fpossible in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
