OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry throughout this period. Some misty
OL,7,Flow cloud may linger at times,
OL,8,Fespecially on Tuesday but otherwise
OL,9,Flengthy sunny periods are expected.
